text: Andre Ulrich Zanga (born 4 April 1997) is a Cameroonian footballer who currently plays for LA Galaxy II in the USL. ==Career== After spending time in the Kadji Sports Academy Zanga signed on loan with LA Galaxy II, a USL affiliate club of LA Galaxy.https://www.lagalaxy.com/post/2017/03/10/la- galaxy-ii-sign-jean-jospin-engola-and-andre-ulrich-zanga-top-cameroonian- academy ==References== ==External links== *Galaxy bio Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Cameroonian footballers Category:Cameroonian expatriate footballers Category:LA Galaxy II players Category:Association football midfielders Category:USL Championship players
